---
title: Honey & Oregano Chicken with Roast Veggie Toss & Pesto Dressing
description: You can't go wrong with honey and oregano, or roasted veggies, or creamy pesto dressing... Know where we're going with this? That's right, this meal is the greatest hits of our favourite flavours, with juicy chicken breast leading the way.

*Keep an eye out...Due to sourcing challenges over the Christmas period, some of the fresh ingredients you receive may be different to what’s pictured. Don’t worry, your recipe will be just as delicious!*
